OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772543468
OL,3,CFamily of girl with bullet in brain
OL,4,Csay 'justice is not enough' after
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FThe family of a nine-year-old girl who
OL,8,Fwas left with a bullet lodged in her
OL,9,Fbrain when she was caught in the
OL,10,Fcrossfire of a gangland shooting in
OL,11,FHackney has said "we lost our child
OL,12,Fand she's not coming back".
OL,14,FSpeaking anonymously to ITV News
OL,15,FLondon in their first interview since
OL,16,Fthe incident, the schoolgirl's parents
OL,17,Fdescribed the devastating impact its
OL,18,Fhad on their lives.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772543468
OL,3,CFamily of girl with bullet in brain
OL,4,Csay 'justice is not enough' after
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,F"It has just shattered our life and we
OL,8,Fcan never join it back the way it was
OL,9,Fbefore," her father said.
OL,11,F"It was just a gang war for them.
OL,13,F"I don't know what benefit they are
OL,14,Fgetting out of all of this but it is
OL,15,Fdestroying common people's life in a
OL,16,Ffraction of second," he added.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772543468
OL,3,CFamily of girl with bullet in brain
OL,4,Csay 'justice is not enough' after
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FThe girl was hit in the head by one of
OL,8,Fsix bullets fired by a gunman on a
OL,9,Fmotorbike, as she sat with her family
OL,10,Fin the Evin Restaurant in Kingsland
OL,11,FHigh Street, Dalston on May 29, 2024.
OL,13,FThe family had been visiting the
OL,14,Fcapital from Birmingham but became the
OL,15,Finnocent victims of a bloody rivalry
OL,16,Fbetween Turkish gangs of north London.
OL,18,FThe shooter has never been caught.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772543468
OL,3,CFamily of girl with bullet in brain
OL,4,Csay 'justice is not enough' after
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FThe family feel that if the gunman is
OL,8,Farrested, it would stop a shooting
OL,9,Flike this from happening to other
OL,10,Fpeople, but would not change what has
OL,11,Fhappened to their daughter.
OL,13,FThey said: "If the cops can bring him
OL,14,Fand give us justice, that's good so
OL,15,Fthat it won't happen to any other
OL,16,Fpeople.
OL,18,F"But personally, we lost our child and
OL,19,Fshe's not coming back... everyone
OL,20,F(forgets) our old child was energetic,
OL,21,Fcapable to do anything...
OL,26,@|D@Apm|D@Ipn
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772543468
OL,3,CFamily of girl with bullet in brain
OL,4,Csay 'justice is not enough' after
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,F"So for us, getting justice is good,
OL,8,Fbut at the same time, I'm giving more
OL,9,Fimportance to my child.
OL,11,F"What will happen to her future? What
OL,12,Fwill happen to her if anything
OL,13,Fhappened to us? She doesn't know how
OL,14,Fto live because of her brain."
OL,16,FWhat we know about the shooting
OL,18,FThe girl was shot in the head when a
OL,19,Fgunman on a motorbike opened fire
OL,20,Fduring "a planned assassination" of
OL,21,Frival North London gang members.
OL,26,@|D@HOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772543468
OL,3,CFamily of girl with bullet in brain
OL,4,Csay 'justice is not enough' after
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FThe intended targets of the shooting
OL,8,Fwere three men who were sat at a
OL,9,Fnearby table in the restaurant.
OL,11,FThey were all injured in the crossfire
OL,12,Fand are said to be affiliated with the
OL,13,FHackney Turks organised crime gang,
OL,14,Fwhich had a rivalry with the Tottenham
OL,15,FTurks.
OL,17,FThe wounded men were taken to Royal
OL,18,FLondon Hospital where each man
OL,19,Funderwent operations for serious
OL,20,Finjuries caused by bullet wounds to
OL,21,Fthigh, leg and backbone respectively.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772543468
OL,3,CFamily of girl with bullet in brain
OL,4,Csay 'justice is not enough' after
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FThe hired spotter and getaway driver,
OL,8,FJavon Riley, who had links with the
OL,9,FTottenham Turks has been jailed for
OL,10,Flife with a minimum term of 34 years
OL,11,Ffor his role in the shooting.
OL,13,FRiley, 33, from Tottenham, north
OL,14,FLondon, was found guilty at the Old
OL,15,FBailey of causing grievous harm with
OL,16,Fintent against the girl and attempting
OL,17,Fto murder three men.
OL,19,FTo this day, the gunman remains at
OL,20,Flarge.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772543468
OL,3,CFamily of girl with bullet in brain
OL,4,Csay 'justice is not enough' after
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FRecalling the event, the girl's mother
OL,8,Fsaid: "Suddenly there was quite a lot
OL,9,Fof noise. At first it sounded like
OL,10,Ffirecracker or a motorbike. There was
OL,11,Flot of noise and chaos all around.
OL,13,F"I went under the table and she went
OL,14,Funder the couch. There were a lot of
OL,15,Fpeople running around.
OL,17,F"I realised she got injured - there
OL,18,Fwas all blood around her and
OL,19,Feverywhere."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772543468
OL,3,CFamily of girl with bullet in brain
OL,4,Csay 'justice is not enough' after
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FAfter the shooting, the schoolgirl
OL,8,Funderwent several intensive operations
OL,9,Fat Great Ormond Street Hospital, with
OL,10,Fthe first being carried out the day
OL,11,Fafter the incident.
OL,13,FThe girl's parents say they watched
OL,14,Ftheir daughter go from a "cheerful
OL,15,Fgirl" who was part of choir,
OL,16,Fgymnastics, fencing, and swimming
OL,17,Fclubs to being unable to walk or speak.
OL,19,F"She didn't open her eyes, she didn't
OL,20,Ftalk.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772543468
OL,3,CFamily of girl with bullet in brain
OL,4,Csay 'justice is not enough' after
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,F"Those were the worst days of our
OL,8,Flife. To see our daughter lying there
OL,9,Fwithout knowing that what's going to
OL,10,Fhappen next," her father said.
OL,12,FThe family had travelled to London on
OL,13,Fa holiday, but now say they'll never
OL,14,Fsee the capital in the same way.
OL,16,F"It's my child's dream to have an ice
OL,17,Fcream near to the London Bridge ... as
OL,18,Ffamilies, everyone goes there because
OL,19,Fthey believe we have cops and laws to
OL,20,Fprotect us - the minimum thing which
OL,21,Fwe would expect to be safe."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772543468
OL,3,CFamily of girl with bullet in brain
OL,4,Csay 'justice is not enough' after
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FWhile the family cope with years of
OL,8,Frehabilitation and therapy for their
OL,9,Fdaughter, they are scared they'll lose
OL,10,Ftheir home and be deported to India.
OL,12,F"We are dealing with the constant fear
OL,13,Fand ambiguity of changing rules and
OL,14,Fchanging visa processes. It is
OL,15,Factually putting immense pressure on
OL,16,Fus, which is beyond our control to
OL,17,Fhandle and it is very hard to explain.
OL,19,F"We want to stay here only for our
OL,20,Fchild's health care, education and her
OL,21,Flife, her future."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772543468
OL,3,CFamily of girl with bullet in brain
OL,4,Csay 'justice is not enough' after
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,FSpeaking at The Old Bailey following
OL,8,Fthe conviction of Javon Riley, the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police said finding the
OL,10,Fgunman is the priority for justice.
OL,12,FOn August 18, 2025, Detective
OL,13,FInspector Ben Dalloway, who led the
OL,14,Finvestigation, said: "Javon Riley's
OL,15,Factions traumatically altered the
OL,16,Ftrajectory of a little girl's life.
OL,18,F"While this outcome serves as a
OL,19,Fslither of justice, the dangerous
OL,20,Findividual responsible for pulling the
OL,21,Ftrigger remains on our streets.
OL,26,@vD@VOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772543468
OL,3,CFamily of girl with bullet in brain
OL,4,Csay 'justice is not enough' after
OL,5,Cshooting
OL,7,F"Those who ordered this shooting are a
OL,8,Fhighly sophisticated criminal
OL,9,Forganisation.
OL,11,F"We understand that people may be
OL,12,Fworried about talking to us because of
OL,13,Fthis, but it is imperative we hear
OL,14,Ffrom anyone who can assist this
OL,15,Finvestigation.
OL,17,F"Justice must be secured for this
OL,18,Flittle girl and her family."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/13
